ygData.subject: RE: Camping Gull
ygData.msgSnippet: Curious... I m 25th now.  Could I handle this island, or should I be at least 27th level?  What level is Gull? From: Paul Heenan
ygData.messageBody:
Curious... I'm 25th now. Could I handle this island, or should I be
at least 27th level? What level is Gull?


From: Paul Heenan <pheenan@...>
Reply-To: EQ-Clerics@onelist.com
To: "'EQ-Clerics@onelist.com'" <EQ-Clerics@onelist.com>
Subject: RE: [EQ-Clerics] Camping Gull
Date: Wed, 26 Jan 2000 10:08:32 -0600


> From: "Don Sheppard" <dshep@...>
>
> How often does he spawn?
7 hours or so

> Do you have to kill other aviaks to get him to
> spawn?
Yes. He has a placeholder. Now, knowing which one is the tricky
part, so you have to "clean" the island.

> Does he always drop the ingot?
Yes.

> Any other tips or info would be
> greatly appreciated.
Best thing to do is to clear the island of all birds then log and
come back 7 hours later. Took me over 2 months to finally get him, and in
that time I went from lvl 27 to 35 =)

Good Luck!

- Drizben D'Vorn, High Priest of Innoruuk
